name: Ousama Ranking Style LoRA
description:
Ousama Ranking style LoRA

Making models can be expensive. Do you like what I do? Consider supporting me on Patreon 🅿️ or feel free to buy me a coffee ☕

The ranking of kings. Oddly fitting that this is the first thing I get to publish since getting to #1 on Civitai. Thank you all for the great support during the last few weeks.

Anyway, this triggers with ousamaranking style and, despite being a style LoRA, can reproduce characters that are very similar to the ones of the anime. However, I was still able to make other characters with it using my other LoRA's. This also excels at making scenery in the style of this anime, that I suggest you check out if you never did.

As for the weight you should go between 0.5 and 0.7. I used Abyss Orange Mix 2 for the examples, but AnyLoRA will work fine too.

The first pic is inpainted from pieces of the last one.

Please enjoy and keep supporting me.


How to use LoRA's in auto1111:

  • Update webui (use git pull like here or redownload it)

  • Copy the file to stable-diffusion-webui/models/lora

  • Select your LoRA like in this video

  • Make sure to change the weight (by default it's :1 which is usually too high)
